title: School's tribute after two teenagers die on Greek island of Ios
description: Two teenage boys have died on the Greek island of Ios.

title: 'More people than ever before' using fake passports and visas to get to UK
description: More people from Iran than ever before are using fake passports or fake visas to get to the UK, an Iranian asylum seeker has told Sky News.

title: The 'double discrimination' fuelling riots and widespread looting in France's second city
description: Anger, resentment, grief - that is the message from Marseille.

title: Grandmother of teenager shot by police in France calls on rioters to stop
description: The grandmother of the French teenager shot by police has called for rioters to "stop" and says her "heart is in pain".

title: 'We love each other': Mayor marries alligator-like reptile who he calls 'princess girl'
description: A mayor in Mexico has married a female alligator-like animal in a traditional ceremony which is believed to bring good fortune to his people.

title: At least two people killed and three critically injured in Baltimore shooting
description: At least two people have been killed and three others have been critically injured after a mass shooting in Baltimore overnight.

title: 'Putin's mistakes' giving US 'once-in-a-generation' chance to recruit Russian spies, says CIA director
description: Dissatisfaction over Vladimir Putin's war in Ukraine, underlined by Wagner boss Yevgeny Prigozhin's armed mutiny, has created a "once-in-a-generation" opportunity for the US to recruit spies, the director of the CIA has said.
